{"tid":917181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"移民衝擊美墨邊境　美方施催淚彈驅散　一度關閉口岸","createTime":"2018-11-26T08:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T09:07:35.000Z","uid":75969,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0d27a390371f054a5095c0e0f19d67a83c0b7b65","tid":917181,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181126/s00005/15769414c44a7c655a4f1fea363e5e08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181126%2Fs00005%2F15769414c44a7c655a4f1fea363e5e08.jpg&h=50faa52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大批打算入境美國申請政治庇護的中美洲移民，周日（25日）聚集並衝擊接壤美國南加州與墨西哥邊境城市蒂華納（Tijuana）的關口。美國邊防人員使用催淚彈驅散群眾，更一度關閉全球其中一個最大的通關入境口岸，導致交通混亂數小時。<br />\n<br />\n據美國有線新聞網絡（CNN），約500名中美洲移民周日下午，試圖衝破美方駐在聖迭戈的聖伊西德羅（San Ysidro Land）入境口岸的防線，美方隨即投擲催淚彈驅散群眾，現場不少人四處逃跑和尖叫，包括孩童和家庭。<br />\n<br />\n美國海關及邊境保衛局表示，該批移民向多名美方邊境人員投擲物件，於是「基於邊境人員的安全風險，他們部署催淚氣體以疏散群眾」。當局在周日一度關閉聖伊西德羅入境口岸，其間多個小時的交通大受影響，直至同日下午才重新開放。<br />\n<br />\n（美國有線新聞網絡）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181126/s00005/1543218254289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181126%2Fs00005%2F1543218254289&d=ihKXy5AFm8UklAqt1nq4Zf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=3acac895\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181126%2Fs00005%2F1543218254289&h=ff368285\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181126/s00005/1543218254289</a>"},{"pid":"2d3c0746de42c441d27aee46a4eba1a1c3e37b61","tid":917181,"uid":26329,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:36:32.000Z","msg":"到底仲要叫ii做移民幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce933fbbd43efe8e95ce4b8ff6fd70139d330f1","tid":917181,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"